left_css -- Version 0.2
By Robin Rainton <robin@rainton.com>
http://rainton.com/fun/freeware

Description
===========
Allows the user to specify a different style sheet for the left
frame (where the folders are listed). Nice if you want that side
smaller than the right.

Usage
=====
Adds a new option to the 'Display Preferences' page where the
'Custom Stylesheet (Left Frame)' can be chosen.

To Do
